##### Links:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------



-5----------------------------------------------------------------------
## Uppercase Letters in Command Mode

C) ~ 	(or    shift + ` )

R) Uppercases the current character


##### Tags:
##### Links:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------





-6----------------------------------------------------------------------
## Undo All Changes to a line

C) U   	(or 	shift u )

R) Undo All Changes to a line
:
:
